                </header>
                <section>
                    <p class="p1"><em>By Marissa Mayer</em></p>
<p class="p1">I am thrilled to announce that award-winning columnist, best-selling author, and TV host David Pogue will be joining Yahoo.Â David will lead a major expansion of consumer tech coverage on Yahoo and will publish columns, blog posts and video stories that demystify the gadgets, apps and technology that powers our usersâ€™ daily lives.</p>
<p class="p1">Yahoo is in a unique positionÂ to bring to life great editorial about the technology consumers are using every day. David is tremendously talented, has a great sense of humor, and is gifted at explaining technology. Â He also just happens to be one of the nicest and most positive people Iâ€™ve met. He has always been one of my favorite journalists, and I canâ€™t think of a better person to make technology more accessible and helpful for the hundreds of millions of people who come to Yahoo every day.</p>
<p class="p2">We canâ€™t wait for David&#8217;s first pieces. In the meantime, here is a taste of the humor, irreverence and know-how that David brings to Yahoo. Enjoy!</p>

